{"tid":410401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【阿媽係女人】WeChat證實將所有個人資料（其實唔止）send俾中共","createTime":"2017-09-23T01:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T14:03:05.000Z","uid":131691,"like":91,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f252735ed913282cbb69229c53887f4b319897dd","tid":410401,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:25:42.000Z","msg":"根據WeChat最新私隱條款，下載呢個騰訊(Tencent)旗下嘅app唔止會將你俾咗permission嘅資料send俾中共，總會將使用細節（包括你嘅contacts嘅個人資料同埋用緊WeChat嘅時候search過嘅嘢）統統上繳中央。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"http://www.moneycontrol.com/news/business/companies/wechat-confirms-that-it-makes-all-private-user-data-available-to-the-chinese-government-2391847.html/news/business/companies/wechat-confirms-that-it-makes-all-private-user-data-available-to-the-chinese-government-2391847.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Fwechat-confirms-that-it-makes-all-private-user-data-available-to-the-chinese-government-2391847.html%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Fwechat-confirms-that-it-makes-all-private-user-data-available-to-the-chinese-government-2391847.html&d=J856HIiPruNH7HKwC4Wa2ARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=e78cb846\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.moneycontrol.com/news/business/companies/wechat-confirms-that-it-makes-all-private-user-data-available-to-the-chinese-government-2391847.html/news/business/companies/wechat-confirms-that-it-makes-all-private-user-data-available-to-the-chinese-government-2391847.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">WeChat permission 列表（截至二零一七年九月廿三號）：</span><br />\n1. 查閱除咗WeChat，電話仲開緊乜嘢其他apps<br />\n2. 無知會情況下下載檔案<br />\n3. 對contacts嘅全權控制（閱讀，搜尋，更改，刪除）<br />\n4. GPS定位<br />\n5. 閱讀你嘅SMS<br />\n6. 查閱你嘅電話號碼<br />\n7. 查閱你電話嘅獨一無二編號（IMEI）<br />\n8. 對任何檔案（包括相，影片）嘅全權控制（閱讀，搜尋，更改，刪除）<br />\n9. 隨時影相／錄影<br />\n10. 隨時錄音<br />\n11. 查閱附近有咩WiFi<br />\n12. 查閱你pair咗嘅脈搏儀，fit sensors等等嘅數據<br />\n13. 全權控制藍牙（pair新裝置，改設定）<br />\n14. 控制WiFi（連線斷線）<br />\n15. 控制音量<br />\n16. 控制NFC<br />\n17. 控制震機<br />\n18. 控制鬧鐘<br />\n19. 更改系統設定"},{"pid":"1a920a62c218fefbec7bd66d1789a5ad92872456","tid":410401,"uid":8040,"like":45,"dislike":2,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:29:49.000Z","msg":"無事嘅<br />\n你唔做衰野就唔會有事<br />\n<br />\n唔裝WeChat 點用微信支付<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 無裝"},{"pid":"e88062d174ce1b63600cc0a0fc4a0395ac60afdd","tid":410401,"uid":23815,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你想點就點<br />\n<br />\n由得D蝗繼續ON99咁用啦"},{"pid":"a12840f9684fbdf7fb168eafec59d94954404b6c","tid":410401,"uid":36445,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:34:34.000Z","msg":"ios既話佢做唔到咁多野啊？"},{"pid":"d93a8ec4048f835efc0da604f16bdff84fbdb072","tid":410401,"uid":1096,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:36:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ios既話佢做唔到咁多野啊？</blockquote><br />\n你個friend用已經將你 contact 比咗大陸"},{"pid":"58d575b5bd0b40ef187b1fb7ac3dfd1aa31b710a","tid":410401,"uid":131691,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:39:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你想點就點<br />\n<br />\n由得D蝗繼續ON99咁用啦</blockquote><br />\n問題係只要一個蝗有你嘅contact，你都已經出事"},{"pid":"9cb6d9b28096eb0f88ffd0470203114c5ce85d18","tid":410401,"uid":470,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:42:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你想點就點<br />\n<br />\n由得D蝗繼續ON99咁用啦</blockquote><br />\n問題係只要一個蝗有你嘅contact，你都已經出事</blockquote><br />\n咁老實講電話號碼做得啲乜<br />\n而且根本無得避"},{"pid":"3448f5336013aeb291c62cb994b4471a44b487be","tid":410401,"uid":111253,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:42:26.000Z","msg":"用過但DEL左係咪都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2abbd5b1ec6436de85fe0c1ed66cbbe0b9d39101","tid":410401,"uid":128014,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:44:59.000Z","msg":"公司電話有we hat,但私人用電話就china app-free <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5d80c9c39d1f62173f24217da3bd63ee9801dc","tid":410401,"uid":131691,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:46:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌你想點就點<br />\n<br />\n由得D蝗繼續ON99咁用啦</blockquote><br />\n問題係只要一個蝗有你嘅contact，你都已經出事</blockquote><br />\n咁老實講電話號碼做得啲乜<br />\n而且根本無得避</blockquote><br />\n你試下上Google同埋Baidu search下幾個朋友嘅電話號碼，睇下搵到啲咩<br />\n有時連地址都搵到"},{"pid":"e26533355222a4f98c83c50315475df7441c870a","tid":410401,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:51:18.000Z","msg":"其實一早都知,只不過係依家明正言順"},{"pid":"963a879f48f54b83636213111cd8bee83326896f","tid":410401,"uid":131691,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:53:35.000Z","msg":"（睇嚟觸動咗中共，全部回覆一致負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"8ce6c82b7d5757af0ee814d37b0cb6754c244ff0","tid":410401,"uid":129601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:55:50.000Z","msg":"android就話做到姐，ios 都比咁多授權？"},{"pid":"88f80465967e13df684a7167d6bb8d5702697736","tid":410401,"uid":131691,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T01:59:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>android就話做到姐，ios 都比咁多授權？</blockquote><br />\n你咪試下囉<br />\n同一個app係Android拎到咁盡<br />\n而且個私隱條款寫到明會咁做（不論Android iO